  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK441">
<l>aṟaṉaṟintu mūtta vaṟivuṭaiyār kēṇmai</l>
<l> tiṟaṉaṟintu tērntu koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (a king) ponder well its value, and secure the friendship of men of virtue and of mature knowledge.</l>
            </lg>
